    },
    {
      "id": "66e31b7daff09e00004a07a7",
      "text": "> #制作難",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159741,
      "updated": 1726159741
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31b7daff09e00004a07a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159741,
      "updated": 1726159741
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31bc5aff09e00004a07bf",
      "text": "いや難しくない？[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159814,
      "updated": 1726159869
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31bf0aff09e00004a07c1",
      "text": "\t[~ 矢印の根元から見る]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159857,
      "updated": 1726159883
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31c0faff09e00004a07c5",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 次のますがヒント？1は「お」]✅",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159887,
      "updated": 1726159973
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31bf0aff09e00004a07c2",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 2は「ん、な、び」　そんなのが答えでいいのか？]✅",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159857,
      "updated": 1726159980
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31bf1aff09e00004a07c3",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 3って謎解きなの？？]？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159857,
      "updated": 1726159986
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31bf1aff09e00004a07c4",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 4: てのした？「す」だね？これでいいの？]✅",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159857,
      "updated": 1726160028
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31bc5aff09e00004a07c0",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 5: 50音なら「と」か]✅",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159814,
      "updated": 1726160051
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31bbbaff09e00004a07bc",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 6: じゃあこれは「ら」なのか]✅",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159804,
      "updated": 1726160096
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31ce0aff09e00004a07c6",
      "text": "\t\t[~ まとめると「おんなび？すとら」いや解答じゃなさそう]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726160096,
      "updated": 1726160136
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31d29aff09e00004a07c7",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 六甲でトラだとタイガースだけど...]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726160170,
      "updated": 1726160187
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31d78aff09e00004a07c8",
      "text": "\t\tわからん！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726160248,
      "updated": 1726160251
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31d7aaff09e00004a07c9",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 3: 「解、て、井」かな]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726160251,
      "updated": 1726160428
    },
    {
      "id": "66e44a39c9ec6a0000654b69",
      "text": "\tわかった！[cak.icon]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1726237246,
      "updated": 1726237253
    },
    {
      "id": "66e44a43c9ec6a0000654b6a",
      "text": "\t ヒント: [~ 6文字ひらがな]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1726237256,
      "updated": 1726239638
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31d7aaff09e00004a07ca",
      "text": "　　　えー、ヒントになってないーw[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726160251,
      "updated": 1726271637
    },
    {
      "id": "66e4d0c9aff09e0000d54607",
      "text": "　　　　いや？そうでもないか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726271689,
      "updated": 1726271694
    },
    {
      "id": "66e4d0cdaff09e0000d54608",
      "text": "　　　　[~ 各問題の答えが1文字だとすると2の答えは「ー」か。3の答えは「け」かな、まとめるとおーけすとら]解けた！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726271694,
      "updated": 1726271856
    },
    {
      "id": "66e31bbbaff09e00004a07bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1726159804,
      "updated": 1726159804
    },
    {
      "id": "69c620ad00000000009183cb",
      "text": "1行まとめ[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774592174,
      "updated": 1774592212
    },
    {
      "id": "69c620ae00000000009183cc",
      "text": "\t[~ 円環状に並んだものの隣接2つで問題が構成される]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774592175,
      "updated": 1774592208
    },
    {
      "id": "69c620d400000000009183ce",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 矢印の開始終了点に実は表現されていた]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774592213,
      "updated": 1774596356
    },
    {
      "id": "69c6310400000000009183d6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
